data.value:
Awesome! We've backed your existing Farms to a new folder we created on your Desktop. Now we can continue installing your Mod Framework.
In Steam; right click on Stardew Valley. In the dropdown, hover over "Manage" and then click "Browse Local Files". Once a window has opened in File Explorer, right click anywhere within the folder and then click "Properties"
Select and copy the entire string of text that appears to the right of "Location" in the "General" tab.
Paste the string of text that you just copied into the textbox below: (it should contain the words "Steam", "steamapps" and "common"
